{"word":"δή","slug":"δή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>δή</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>ἤ-δη, ἐπει-δή, δῆτα</el> (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δή\">δή</a></el> + -<el>τα</el>, like <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἶτα\">εἶτα</a></el>) ‘indeed’] an emphatic marker focusing one’s attention on a matter at hand <b><i>well then, right now</i> <a href='B:490 2:15'>Lk 2:15</a>; <a href='B:510 6:3'>Ac 6:3</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 13:2'>13:2</a>; <a href='B:510 15:36'>15:36</a>; <a href='B:530 6:20'>1 Cor 6:20</a>;</b> <el>ὃς <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δή\">δή</a></el> <i>who, note well!</i> or <i>who really</i> <b><a href='B:470 13:23'>Mt 13:23</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐ\">οὐ</a> γὰρ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δήπου\">δήπου</a></el> <i>for certainly not</i> <b><a href='B:650 2:16'>Hb 2:16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:δέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δηλαυγῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}